# Links for QA Scenario

* [System Under Test](http://rest-accachallenge.rhcloud.com/resources/fixture-finder/html/FixtureFinder.html)

If you don't have a Github account yet, quickly create one [here](https://github.com/join) or use the following account  _EmbeddedTester (Password provided in the room)_

***

# Links for Embedded Scenario 

* [Github for Embedded Scenario](https://github.com/EmbeddedTestingWorkshop/Embedded_FixtureFinder)

# Upload your solution

* [If you want, you can upload your solution to Google Drive](https://drive.google.com/folderview?id=0B2Rm2EYEiEkffmN4WTU2ak9GUi16dnU5VHhQWUhKVWJGejIzNGFodWxwLXR3eTFYeWJEeFU)
* If you don't have a gooogle account, you can use this account _EmbeddedTesterWorkshop (Password provided in the room)_

***

# Feedback 

It would be great if you can give us feedback after the workshop:
* [Feedback Survey](https://www.surveymonkey.com/s/LQD67KJ)
